prompts.text: A ginger cat sits at a small table in a bustling, slightly worn cafeteria. It delicately holds a miniature teacup with its paw, its eyes focused intently on the warm liquid. The steam from the teacup swirls in the soft, warm light. Surrounding the cat, blurred figures of humans and other animals create a whimsical, surreal scene. The colors are muted and warm, conveying a sense of comfort and everyday charm. A high-quality, cinematic shot captures this moment.
